Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:20.48,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(640,600)\an7\pos(544,692)\fnFZYaSongS-DB-GB\fs40}因为“哈姆奈特”与“哈姆雷特”事实上是同一名字\N在16世纪末至17世纪初的斯特拉特福档案中可以互换使用\N\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h-- 《哈姆奈特之死与〈哈姆雷特〉的渊源》\N\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\fs30}译注: 出自著名莎士比亚学者斯蒂芬·格林布拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:23.06,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(320,320)\fnFZYaSongS-DB-GB\pos(960,580)\fs40\i1\c&HE7E7E8&}字幕译制\N{\fs60\i0}蒙太奇字幕组
Comment: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:20.48,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(640,600)}【译注: 出自著名莎士比亚学者斯蒂芬·格林布拉特】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了\NThere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧 你是饿坏了吧\NThere. You were hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,乖孩子\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:30.80,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在朗读《农事诗》第三卷】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:37.37,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《农事诗》: 维吉尔(古罗马诗人)农业诗篇 论耕作与农事纷争】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）...终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,继续念\NRepeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NGood day, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,姑娘好\NGood day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你到休兰农场来做什么？\NWhat brings you to Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里教孩子们\NI'm tutoring the boys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,教拉丁的先生啊\NThe Latin tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说过你\NI've heard of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那你来这园里干什么？\NWhat brought you into the garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我就随口问问 教书先生\NIt's just a question, master tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我 那个...\NYes, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是出来透透气 而且...\NI suppose the air was fresh out here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我看到你带着只鸟\Nuh, I saw you with your bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是只鹰 - 哦\N- It's a hawk. - Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,能上前看看吗？\NMay I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,别凑太近\NDon't get too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他不认识你\NHe doesn't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 小家伙\NHello, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 哈哈哈\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜欢你\NHe likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？\NWhat is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,莫打听\NI shan't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,偏打听\NYou shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不说\NI shan't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你会说的 - 我不会\N- You shall. - I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等我亲你时你就会说了\NYou'll tell me when we kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫安妮丝\NMy name is Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你家在哪里？\NWhere are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我说错话了吗？\NHave I said something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啊？ - 没有\N- Huh? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不知道我是谁 - 等下 我想去你...\N- You don't know who I am. - Wait, I wish to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你别再来找我了\NYou can't see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了？\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我在地里帮巴塞洛缪\NI was in the field helping Bartholomew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小羊崽病了\NA newborn lamb is unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好... 我也去了地里\NWell, I... I went to the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可没见到你\NI did not see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实在那儿 巴塞洛缪哥 你给她说说\NWell, I was there. Tell her, Bartholomew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她确实在那里\NShe was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过新来的教拉丁那位先生吗？\NHave you seen the new Latin tutor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是皮匠的儿子\NThe glover's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们说他上着上着课跑掉了 就再没回来\NThe boys said he just ran out, never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他是来教书还债的\NHe was supposed to give them lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还他父亲的债\Nto pay off his father's debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我没见过他\NI haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也罢 早该料到\NWell, should've known better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,父子都一个德行\NLike father, like son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩可是咱们教区最美的姑娘\NYou know, I do believe you are the prettiest girls in the parish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 将来...\N- We are. - One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,会有许多人上门提亲 我会亲自把关\NI shall have my wits about me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,准把你们嫁个好人家\Nfor all the suitors that will come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝是大姐 还轮不到我们\NAgnes is the eldest. She'll marry first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她成天往树林里跑 像个流浪女\NShe will not if she keeps running off to the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会娶她？\Nlike a gypsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了?\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等你等了好几个钟头\NWe were expecting you hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在... - 说啊\N- I was... - Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我在忙活\NI was working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\NSit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,快坐下吧\NSit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,饭菜都凉了\NYour supper's near cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别闹 别闹 - 别抢\N- Uh, boys, boys! - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 住手 - 大家都有份 别抢\N- Stop. - There's enough for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,休兰农场那边教得怎么样？\NHow go the lessons at Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那些孩子不是读书的料\NThose boys are no scholars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我就纳闷 他们读书有啥用 - 嗯\N- I wonder at the notion of all that learning. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,注定务农的孩子学拉丁文？\NLatin for boys who will be naught but sheep farmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为了摆谱吗？ - 不 不 不\N- It is the putting on of airs. - No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 够了 - 都给你 吉尔伯特\N- That will do! - All right, Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,听你娘的 都有份别争\NYou heard your mother. There's enough for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你说休兰那帮孩子不好\NYou speak ill of the boys at Hewlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“不是读书的料”\N"They're no scholars."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可我告诉你\NBut I tell you something,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们将来比你更像个男子汉\Nthey'll ever be more of a man than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,人家将来有正经活 可你没有\NThey are put to honest work, unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你没出息 没手艺 只会摆谱\NUseless, tradeless, your fancy airs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,读那么多书\NAll that education,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一点用都没有\Nnot an ounce of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我这没出息的去教书\NI'm tutoring those boys to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是替你还那户人家的债吗？\Nyour debts to that family, am I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你欠休兰家那么多债\NYour immeasurable amount of debt to that family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是我... 住手\NI'm not... Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,休兰那边其他人\NWhat of the rest of the family at Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你都见过吗？\NHave you met them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只见过那户的母亲\NThe mother only.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那大女儿没见到吗？ - 没有\N- Not the eldest daughter? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都说 那姑娘是森林巫婆的后代 \NIt is said the girl is the child of a forest witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我就见过 她独自走在山路上\NI've seen her, wandering the back roads alone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,臂上还有只鹰\Nwith a hawk on her arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,休兰那儿还有鹰？\NA hawk at Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,传言说她每次进林都是一个人带着那只鹰\NThey say she takes him to the forest with her unaccompanied.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗 伊莱莎？\NYeah, but are you certain, Eliza?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那拿着鹰的是长女 不是仆人？\NThe eldest daughter keeps a hawk, not a servant girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是仆人 我确定\NYes. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这里做什么？\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,带了个东西给你\NBrought you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是...\NIt's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,给你那只鸟的新手套\Nit's a new glove for your bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我有手套\NI have a glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 别走\NAgnes, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是谁\NI know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是谁？\NWho am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧...不算认识你 只是听过些传言...\NWell, I... I don't know you, but I've heard things...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,说我是森林巫婆的女儿？\NI'm the daughter of a forest witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 村里这么说 但我 我不在意...\NYes. People say that, but I-I don't care...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是我母亲的女儿\NI am my mother's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,从她那儿学的本事多着呢\NI've learnt many things from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你在看什么？\NWhat are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你 - 为什么？\N- You. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 因... - 你这教书的先生 不该能言善辩吗？\N- I... -I thought you were a man of words, master tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 难道你不是吗？ - 只是...\N- Are you not? - Jus...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时很难直接跟人说话\NSpeaking with people is sometimes difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那就讲个故事吧\NWell, tell me a story, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 讲故事？ - 对\N- A story? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你想听什么故事？\NWhat story would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,讲个能打动你自己的故事\NSomething that moves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道俄耳甫斯和欧律狄刻的故事吗？\NDo you know the story of Orpheus and Eurydice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.68,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 古希腊神话】
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,俄耳甫斯这个男人\NOrpheus is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有着天赋异禀的音乐才能\Na man of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他还有着天籁般的嗓音\NHe has this exquisite voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他弹那种七弦里拉...\NHis playing of the kithara, which is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是类似竖琴的乐器\Nis-is a harp-like lyre,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,声音美得不可思议\Nis so divine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,连天上的鸟儿...\Nbirds, the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,地上的走兽 甚至石头和树\Nthe beasts, e-even the stones and the trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,都能被他的音乐打动随之起舞\Nthey all moved to the rhythm of his music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,后来 俄耳甫斯爱上了一位美丽的山林少女 叫欧律狄刻\NNow, Orpheus falls in love with this beautiful nymph, Eurydice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和山林少女刚结完婚\NSoon after their marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她就被毒蛇咬了\NEurydice's bitten by a viper
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,毒素在她体内迅速扩散\Nand poison courses through her body,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她就此身亡\Nand she's killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,俄耳甫斯悲痛欲绝\NAnd Orpheus, filled with grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,下到冥府想要将她带回\Njourneys to the underworld to take her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:14:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他用琴声迷住了守门的三头犬刻耳柏洛斯\NHe charms this three-headed dog, Cerberus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至感动了冥王哈得斯\NHe beguiles Hades until finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,最终冥王同意了\N...he's allowed to take his love back with him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,允许把这名女子带回人间 但...\Nto the world of the living but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一个条件\N...under one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么条件？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这名女子必须跟在他身后\NShe must follow behind him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而他绝对不能回头看\Nand he must not turn around to look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 他们开始往人间走\NNow, as they begin their ascent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,俄耳甫斯却听不见他妻子的脚步声\NOrpheus can't hear her footsteps, so he listens...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,于是他一直听 一直听 一直听\N...and listens and listens and listens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他只听见了自己的心跳\NBut all he can hear is the sound of his heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,其余是一片寂静\NAnd the rest is silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,当他快到冥门出口时...\NAnd as he approaches the gates of the underworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他忍不住了\N...he can't contain himself any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他回头去看妻子 然后妻子...\NHe turns around to look at her, and she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,永远被困在冥府里了\N...trapped in the underworld forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个好故事\NThat was a good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗？\NDid you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,艾草者 古之名药也\NRemember, mugwort, what you brought to pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:43.75,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《九草咒》: 古英语药咒 列九种草药以驱毒治疫】
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,世人皆知其德 传颂至今\Nwhat you readied at Regenmeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,其名曰艾 为草之首\NYou're called Una, the most ancient plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,能驱三疾 能制三十疾\NYou defy three, you defy 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,能解毒气 能散瘴疠\Nyou defy venom, you defy air illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,能降瘟疫 克之而胜\Nyou defy the horror that stalks the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,车前草者 草之母也\NAnd you, waybread, plant mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,根植东方 性禀刚毅\Nyou're open to the east yet mighty within.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,遭车碾而不折 遇众踏而复起\NCarts creeped over you, women rode over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,刚柔相济 疗人间之疾苦\NYou withstood it all, and you pushed back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的能靠摸一个人的手\NIs it true that you know everything about a person
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看透一切吗？\Nby touching them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不是全部\NNot everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你摸我时你看到了什么？\NWhen you touched me here, what did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见了一幅画面\NI saw a landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一幅画面？ - 嗯\N- You saw a landscape? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,空洞 黑洞 裂口\NSpaces, caves, cliff tops,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,暗道和深海\Ntunnels and oceans,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,深不见底 一片漆黑的虚空\Nthis deep, dark, black void,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,未知的国度\Nundiscovered countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）天道有常 宿命有律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.30,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在朗读《农事诗》第一卷】
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）万物难逃衰落之数 消亡乃其必然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）天道有常 宿命有律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）万物难逃衰落之数 消亡乃其必然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她说话了...\NShe speaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她说话了 她说话了\NShe speaks, she speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,且慢\NBut, soft,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那窗户透出来的是什么光？\Nwhat light through yonder window breaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:16.83,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在创作《罗密欧与朱丽叶》第二幕第二场】
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那是东方 朱丽叶就是太阳...\NIt is the east, and Juliet is the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...赶走那....\N...and kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...嫉妒的月亮\N...the envious moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和你成亲\NI wish to be handfasted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我 我必须和你成亲\NNo, I... I must be handfasted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,非你不可\NNo one else will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去跟你继母和你哥哥说\NI-I will speak with your stepmother and your brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,估计他们不会答应\Nand of course they will not agree, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不管行不行就这么定了 不能等了\NI don't care because I have no talent for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是私定终身\NI cannot abide waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那你父母怎么办？\NWhat about your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们绝不会答应的\NYour parents will never agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\NFollow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等 等 等\NWait. Wait. W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跑不掉了 - 别\N- No! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手套\NMy glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是我母亲留给我的 - 哦\N- This is my mother's glove. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她源于丛林\NShe came out of the woods...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就像她母亲一样\N...like her mother
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,像她母亲的母亲一样\Nand her mother before her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我家族女人能看到些...\NThe women in my family see things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,别人看不到的东西\N...that others don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,艾草者 古之名药也\NRemember, mugwort,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,世人皆知其德 传颂至今\Nwhat you brought to pass, what you readied at Regenmeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其名曰艾 为草之首\NYou're called Una, the most ancient plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,能驱三疾 能制三十疾\NYou defy three, you defy 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,能解毒气 能散瘴疠\Nyou defy venom, you defy air illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能降瘟疫 克之而胜\Nyou defy the horror that stalks the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,巴塞洛缪 会好的\NBartholomew, it will heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,会留疤吗？\NWill it make a scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会 但并非坏事\NIt may. That's no bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,听\NListen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,听见了么？\NDo you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,留心你的梦 安妮丝\NYou must pay attention to your dreams, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,梦永远会指引你\NThey will always guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们好 - 你也好\N- Good day. - Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 你怎么在...\NAgnes, what's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么在这儿？\Nwhat's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她母亲把她逐出家门了\NHer mother has banished her from their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是我亲生母亲\NShe's not my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那房子归我哥哥巴塞洛缪管\NThe house belongs to my brother, Bartholomew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我是自愿离开的\NI chose to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她有身孕了\NShe's with child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还说孩子是你的\NSays it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗？真是你的吗？ - 呃...\N- Is it? Yours? - Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她肚子里的孩子 是你弄的吗？\NThe child in her belly, did you put it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们已经私定了 娘 - 休想\N- We are handfasted, Mother. - We will never allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这有什么错啊 - 没我们的同意\N- There is no sin in it. - I'm afraid you will need
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你成不了亲的 - 这有什么错啊\N- our consent, and we will... - There is no sin in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们决不允许这桩婚事 - 行 行\N- ...we will never give it, ever! - All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你被她蛊惑了 - 不是的\N- You've been bewitched. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁愿你当水手送命 也别娶这个巫婆\NI'd rather you went to sea than marry this wench.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽\NMary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不必这样\NThere's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,既然他们情投意合 这事好解决\NI have no doubt we can come to an arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 约翰 - 安静 女人\N- John. - Hush, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定想在教堂里\NI am certain you are eager
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你妹妹出嫁吧\Nto see your sister before the altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.41,0:23:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在肯定要\NI'm certain you'd rather not see your boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,控告你儿子奸淫\Ndragged before the bawdy court.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要闹成那样\NThere's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们两厢情愿 已经私定了\NThey said they are handfasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.27,0:23:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁不嫁由我说了算\NOnly if I say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁给那白面书生到底有啥好处？他有什么用\NBut why marry a pasty-faced scholar? What use is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.19,0:23:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他的内心比我见过的任何人都深邃\NHe's got more inside of him than any man I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,人心是会变的\NEverything will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你也不例外\NYou. You will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心已经变了\NI'm already changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,里头太静了\NIt's too quiet in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哪儿里头？\NIn where?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们家\NThat house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,记得我们害怕迷茫时 娘怎么劝咱的吗？\NWhat would our mother say to us if we were afraid or uncertain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.63,0:23:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要敞开心扉\NTo live with our hearts open.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫它躲在黑暗里\NTo shut it not in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要走向太阳 去拥抱那温暖\Nbut to turn it to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他爱的是我本色 不图我变成谁\NHe loves me for what I am, not what I ought to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:23:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就嫁给他吧\NThen marry him you shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,艾草者 古之名药也\NRemember, mugwort...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.54,0:24:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,来 说跟我一起说 一起说\NSay it with me. Say it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,世人皆知其德\NWhat you brought to pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,传颂至今\Nwhat you readied at Regenmeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,其名曰艾 为草之首\NYou are called Una, the most ancient plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.32,0:24:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,能驱三疾 能制三十疾\NYou defy three, you defy 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.13,0:24:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能解毒气 能散瘴疠\Nyou defy venom, you defy air illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.85,0:24:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能降瘟疫 克之而胜\Nyou defy the horror that stalks the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.33,0:25:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,回头看我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.18,0:25:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,回头看我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.66,0:27:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.36,0:29:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.11,0:29:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看 看那光 那是火\NLook. Look at that. Look at the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.98,0:29:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看看 那是什么啊\NMmm, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.39,0:29:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,小狗叼进来个东西\NThe doggy dragged something in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.36,0:29:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看看\NThere's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.79,0:29:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.99,0:29:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸回来了\NDaddy's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.90,0:29:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.15,0:30:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,针脚要小一点\NStitches need to be smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.26,0:30:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再小一点\NM-Much smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.44,0:30:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.36,0:30:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哼\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.68,0:30:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没出息\NUseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.37,0:30:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好 再小点\NOkay, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.19,0:30:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,再小点\Nsmaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.30,0:30:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪儿？ - 我要出去\N- Where are you going? - I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.75,0:30:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,回去干活\NGet back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.04,0:30:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你最后一次打我\NThat was the last time you will ever hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.65,0:30:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.18,0:30:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白吗？ - 明白\N- Do you understand?! - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.36,0:31:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,郎君 上床睡觉吧\NMy love, you should come back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.96,0:31:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你在写什么？\NWhat are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.11,0:31:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不值一提\NNothing of note.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.12,0:31:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,总有值得称道的地方\NIt's never nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.67,0:31:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还没写好呢\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.31,0:31:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也许写完会好...\NPerhaps when it's finished, it will...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.29,0:31:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\NPerhaps when it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.68,0:31:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,念给我听听吧\NWhy don't you read me what you've written?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.09,0:31:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 这还没...\NA-Agnes, it's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.63,0:31:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还没写好呢\NIt-It's not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.92,0:31:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没写好\NIt's not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.96,0:31:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别敲了 吵醒孩子了\NStop it. You'll wake the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.55,0:31:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.54,0:32:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不哭 不哭\NNo. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.47,0:32:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.53,0:32:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝多了\NI've had too much, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.56,0:32:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 我喝多了\NAgnes, I've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.16,0:32:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝...\NI've had...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.51,0:32:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝的太多了\NI've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.41,0:32:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.15,0:32:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事放不下吗？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.03,0:32:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你看看手相\NGive me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.70,0:32:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别 别 别 别\NPl-Pl-Please, please, please, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.75,0:32:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别 求你了 别\Nplease, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.53,0:32:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怕我看见什么吗？ - 求你了 别\N- What are you afraid I will see? - Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.22,0:32:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕我将来会伤害你\NThat I am a violent and dangerous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.36,0:32:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不会 你不是那样的人\NNo, you are none of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.77,0:32:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么能肯定？ - 你是个好人 你是个...\N- How do you know? - You're a good man. You're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.20,0:32:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好人\NYou are a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.74,0:33:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好人\NYou're a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.04,0:33:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是后悔跟我结婚了吗？\NIs it that you wish that we never wed?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.74,0:33:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能说出这种话？\NHow could you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.16,0:33:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能说出这种话？\NHow could you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.54,0:33:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我活着就是为了你和苏珊娜\NYou and Susanna are all that I live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.89,0:33:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我活着就是为了你们\NAll that I live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.70,0:33:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那到底怎么回事？ - 是...\N- What is it, then? - This...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.91,0:33:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来 把手给我 - 停下\N- Here. Look at me. - Just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.88,0:33:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,停 停 求你停下 停 停 停\NStop, stop. Please, please, please, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.76,0:33:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.31,0:33:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 听着 听我说\NListen. Listen. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.37,0:33:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我迷失了\NI'm lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.92,0:33:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不...\NI've lost my...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.10,0:33:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到方向了\NI've lost my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.93,0:34:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要 我需要静下心好好写作 安妮丝\NI just need to-- uh, Agnes, I just need to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.73,0:34:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他觉都睡不着\NHe's not sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.61,0:34:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他对你发过火吗？ - 没有\N- Has he ever lost his temper with you? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.23,0:34:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 要是他对你动手.... - 没有 他从没那样 从没那样\N- If he raises a hand... - No, he has never. He's never.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.93,0:34:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是为自己懊恼\N He's angry with himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.14,0:34:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,心里难受得要命\NHe's sick with himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.45,0:34:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个好人\NHe's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.72,0:34:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好丈夫 也是个好父亲\NHe's a good husband, he's a good father,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.15,0:34:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但他还需要更多\Nbut he n-needs more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.14,0:34:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经有了家和你 他还能需要什么？\NWhat could he possibly need other than his family and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.54,0:34:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他已经有了你 - 他需要去伦敦\N- He has you. - He needs to go to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.87,0:34:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 伦敦？ - 是的\N- London? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.85,0:34:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥去伦敦？ \NWhy London?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.72,0:34:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为伦敦汇聚天下\NBecause London is where the whole world gathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.99,0:34:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定能把他爹的手艺带去发扬光大\NPerhaps he could extend his father's business there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.96,0:34:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哎 你又冲动了 - 谁知道他将来会怎样\N- Oh, you're being hasty again. - Who knows what he may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.60,0:34:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是冲动 他需要更多\NI'm not being hasty. He needs more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.31,0:34:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他只是太闲了 - 他不该呆这小地方\N- Well, he needs proper work. - He's not of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.27,0:34:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给他找个活儿忙起来\NThe man needs proper work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.66,0:34:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这小地方能有什么出路？ -  他不能就这么跑掉\N- What's in this little town? - He can't just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.14,0:34:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这小日子 这小地方...\NThis little life? This little thing, it'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.94,0:34:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,会压垮他的\N...crush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.26,0:34:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他得离他爹远点\NHe needs distance from his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.15,0:34:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟他一起去伦敦吗？\NAnd you would go with him to London?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.43,0:34:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不 等他安顿好再说\NNo, I'll wait until he's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.32,0:34:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,马上家里就会多一口人\NThere'll be more of us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.86,0:34:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 又怀上了？ - 是的\N- Another child? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.80,0:34:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,夏末时候生\NBy summer's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.17,0:35:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那现在更不能把他送走了\NThen now is not the time to send him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.76,0:35:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我会失去他的\NI'll lose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.07,0:35:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经在失去他了\NI'm already losing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.52,0:35:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要是送他走 就彻底失去他了\NYou'll lose him if you send him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.64,0:35:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不会的 我肯定我俩的爱能维系得住\NNo, I know, I know that our love will keep us steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.15,0:35:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 替我跟他爹说说吧\NPlease. Will you speak to his father?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.82,0:35:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你跟他提去伦敦的事 他会听你的\NHe'll listen to you if you suggest him going to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.84,0:35:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.52,0:35:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我得找个住处\NI should find lodgings.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.91,0:35:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,最好靠河的 离河边皮革场近点\NBe near the river, close to the tanneries.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.44,0:35:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说那河水很急\NBut I'm told that the currents in the river are dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.13,0:35:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,过河要请有经验的船夫\Nand that you must engage an experienced boatman
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.21,0:35:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,每次过河我都照办\Nevery time you cross, and I'll be certain to do that every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.53,0:35:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.11,0:35:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我会时时想念你和苏珊娜\NAnd I will think of you and Susanna
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.73,0:35:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一刻也不会忘了你们\Nwith every passing moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.26,0:35:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给咱们找个好住处\NAnd I will find us lodgings in London,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.84,0:35:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候在伦敦团聚\Nand we shall all be together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.69,0:35:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没预见出是男孩还是女孩吗？\NDo you still not know if it's a boy or a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.07,0:35:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.21,0:35:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我也说不清为什么\NDon't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.54,0:35:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说过会有两个孩子陪你到最后吗？\NHave you not said that you would always have two children?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.48,0:35:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.08,0:36:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,临终前会有两个孩子在身边\NTwo children at my deathbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.90,0:36:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,第二个能陪你到最后的人来了\NWell, then, here is the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.96,0:36:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱们就别道别了 - 好\N- We won't say goodbye. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.91,0:36:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不早了 快走吧\NYou get-- Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.42,0:37:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要出门吗？ - 不是 我只是...\N- You going somewhere? - No, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.99,0:37:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我要去湖边走走...\NYes, I'm going to the lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.94,0:37:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你不许进森林\NYou're not going to the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.61,0:37:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我非去不可 - 不 你不许去 吉尔伯特快来\N- I must. - No, you must not. Gilbert!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.03,0:37:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你...你得让我去那里\NYou... you have to let me go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.08,0:37:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你必须让我走 - 听我说 安妮丝\N- Let me go there! - Listen Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.10,0:37:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你得放我去 - 河堤已经决口了\N- You must let me go! - The river has burst its banks!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.64,0:37:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我去 - 外面很危险\N- Let me! - There is no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.88,0:37:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 根本没路去森林那边 - 放我走 不要\N- There's no way to get to the forest. - Let me! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.73,0:37:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们都为你准备好了 - 我孩子\N- We have everything ready for you. - My baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.38,0:37:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我 我孩子\NNo, my-my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.46,0:37:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.21,0:37:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,生不出来\NIt isn't coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.45,0:37:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法在这屋里生孩子\NI will not have my baby in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.90,0:37:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没法在这屋\NNot in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.51,0:37:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没法\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.11,0:37:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,河水\NThe river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.36,0:37:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 用力 用力 用力 - 不 不 不\N- Hush, hush, hush, hush. Hush. - No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.76,0:37:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他说要住河边\NHe spoke about the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.99,0:38:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,河很危险 他可能会被冲走\NThe river is dangerous. He may be swept downstream!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.35,0:38:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 安妮丝\NAgnes. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.71,0:38:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 安妮丝 他一切安好\NAgnes. Agnes, all is well with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.75,0:38:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道忘了他最近的信吗？\NDo you not recall his last letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.93,0:38:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫了\NStop the screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.07,0:38:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,会把整村人都吵醒的\NYou'll wake the whole town.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.28,0:38:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他语气...\NHe sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.41,0:38:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他语气不对\NHe sounded different.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.03,0:38:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他带来的是好消息\NNo, he had good news for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.24,0:38:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 剧场 - 剧场\N- The theater. - Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.54,0:38:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他和剧团签了合约\NHe has a contract with the players
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.99,0:38:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 做剧场用的手套 - 剧场\N- to make gloves for the theater. - the theater
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.55,0:38:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 用力\NAgnes, hush now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.47,0:38:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,用力 用力 用力\NHush. Hush. Hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.87,0:38:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,用力挤 用力挤\NBear down. Bear down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.14,0:38:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来了 来了\NAh! Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.22,0:38:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 出来了 - 是个男孩\N- There we go. - It's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.08,0:38:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真好\NThere we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.39,0:38:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,乖孩子 乖孩子\NGood boy. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.02,0:38:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是个男孩\NIt's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.29,0:38:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是个男孩\NIt's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.66,0:38:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子\NMy boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.52,0:38:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.36,0:39:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？怎么了？\NWhat is it? What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.50,0:39:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她又要生了\NShe's starting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.69,0:39:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 孩子啊 你怀的是双胞胎 - 来 伊莱莎\N- You're having twins, my girl. - Come on, Eliza.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.89,0:39:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快 抱着他\NHere. Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.38,0:39:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,抱好\NTake him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.67,0:39:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\NNo, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.10,0:39:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我临终前会有两个孩子在身边\NTwo standing at my deathbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.97,0:39:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为...\NI always believed that it would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.90,0:39:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以为是长大的孩子\Nthat they would be my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.94,0:39:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我...\NAnd now...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.67,0:39:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了 原来就是你们俩\Nnow I see it will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.43,0:39:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,得把你扶到产凳上\NWe need to get you to the stool.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.78,0:39:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快生了 要生了\NIt's coming. It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.16,0:39:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要 - 来 来 起来 起来\N- No. - Come on. Come on up. Up, up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.33,0:39:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别 我 我不行\NPlease. I can't... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.45,0:39:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.68,0:39:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来 - 我不该...\N- Go. - I should never have...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.72,0:39:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了...\NI can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.74,0:39:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我挺不过去了\NI can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.19,0:40:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我弄错了 我弄错了\NI got it wrong. I got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.08,0:40:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我弄错...\NI got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.38,0:40:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他不在\NHe... He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.82,0:40:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他不在这里\NHe's... He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.08,0:40:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 你能行的\NAgnes, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.38,0:40:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须行\Nand you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.25,0:40:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行\NI cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.02,0:40:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.38,0:40:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你能行的\NYou can...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.17,0:40:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你会挺过去的\Nand you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.06,0:40:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫就在这间屋里出生\NYour husband was born here in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.44,0:40:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在那窗边 第一次吸气\NHe took his first breath there by the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.03,0:40:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.19,0:40:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 保住孩子\NPlease let this child live.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.08,0:40:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一定保孩子 一定\NLet this child live. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.95,0:40:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,让他....\NWill you let him...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.62,0:40:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,让他回到家后有孩子能陪他\NLet him come back and be with his child.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.50,0:40:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.96,0:40:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,让他对我留个好念想\NLet him think kindly of me always.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.45,0:40:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了我\NRemember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.07,0:40:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,娘\NMama.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.36,0:40:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,娘\NMama.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.70,0:41:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,娘？\NMum?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.39,0:41:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她没抗住\NJust too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.19,0:41:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她承受了很大的痛苦\NShe was in too much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.36,0:41:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太可怜了\NI mean, poor woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.70,0:41:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越痛 她承受不住了\NShe just got weaker and weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.96,0:41:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候命就是这样\NI mean, that's just the way of it sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.48,0:41:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她 她大概早就知道这一刻了\NShe-she must have known the end was nigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.22,0:41:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,最好别跟孩子提起她了\NBest not speak of her to the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.10,0:41:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,再娶一个吧\NSafer with a different mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.60,0:41:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子都还小\NSo young.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.64,0:41:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,兴许能忘掉\NThey may not remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.74,0:41:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 娘 - 安妮丝 安妮丝\N- Mum! - Agnes. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.51,0:41:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 娘 不要 - 不 不 安妮丝\N- Mama, no! - No, no. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.46,0:41:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子 孩子\NChild. Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.85,0:41:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 娘 不要 - 不 不 孩子 孩子 不行\N- Mummy, no! - No, no, no. Ch-Ch-Ch-- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.25,0:41:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放开我 - 不行\N- No! - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.47,0:41:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 让我见娘 - 不 不\N- No, let me see her! - No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.56,0:41:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要见娘 - 不\N- Let me see her! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.24,0:41:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 娘\NNo, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.88,0:41:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 安妮丝 - 不\N- Agnes. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.95,0:41:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,娘 我要我娘 我要我娘\NMum. I want, I want my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.81,0:41:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我要我娘啊...\NI want my mum...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.65,0:42:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来了 是个女孩\NOh! Here we go! It's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.54,0:42:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是个女孩 她...\NIt's a girl. She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.91,0:42:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等等... - 怎么了？\N- It's... Wait. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.59,0:42:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点\NCome on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.85,0:42:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么不哭？\NWhy is she not crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.90,0:42:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么不哭？\NWhy is she not crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.79,0:42:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她没活过来\NShe lives not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.65,0:42:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让我抱抱\NLet me have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.67,0:42:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 这不吉利\NYou should not look upon her. It's bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.49,0:42:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,把她给我\NGive her to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.48,0:42:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把她安葬妥当的\NI'll make sure it gets a decent burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.68,0:42:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,把我孩子给我\NGive me my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.11,0:42:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子啊\NMy child.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.62,0:42:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 你有个儿子\NAgnes, you have a baby boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.24,0:43:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他抱来 你可以喂他\NLet me bring him to you, and you may feed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.98,0:43:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩已经去了天国\NThe girl has gone to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.98,0:43:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她不会去天国的\NShe's not gone to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.86,0:43:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲去世那晚我发过誓\NI made a vow the night my mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.25,0:43:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去你们的教堂 去了也什么都不说\NI will go to your church, but I shan't say a word there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.34,0:44:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 太好了 太好了\NYes. Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.72,0:44:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活下去\NYou will live.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.56,0:44:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活下去\NYou will live.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.53,0:44:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保护你到底 绝不放手\NI will make sure nothing ever takes you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.63,0:44:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么都找不到\NI actually couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.00,0:44:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.24,0:45:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.61,0:45:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\NPerfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.85,0:45:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,找到帽子了\NI found my hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.18,0:45:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来 对\NOkay. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.47,0:45:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来 转过去 转过去\NOkay, take that side. Take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.70,0:45:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.14,0:45:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后系好\NAnd put it around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.55,0:45:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,完美\NPerfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.25,0:45:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哎呀 - 我来吧\N- Ooh. Sorry. - Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.43,0:45:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,挡到我脸了\NIt's down my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.09,0:45:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟我学我是哈姆奈特 - 我是哈姆奈特\N- I'm Hamnet. - I'm Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.13,0:45:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是珠迪丝 - 我是珠迪丝\N- I'm Judith. - I'm Judith.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.81,0:46:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,屋里不准跑\NThere will be no running in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.39,0:46:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要举止端正 要像...\NConduct yourselves, please, as...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.13,0:46:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,淑女与绅士\Ngentlewomen and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.39,0:46:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要去哪儿？\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.82,0:46:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对 他来了 他来了\NYeah. He's-he's coming. He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.50,0:46:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,回来了\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.59,0:46:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.57,0:46:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,明摆着他俩对调了衣服\NWe all know they've swapped clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.63,0:46:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们什么时候揭穿？\NHow long are we going to pretend we don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.42,0:46:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他们继续演 咱们就不揭穿\NWe'll pretend for as long as they think they're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.59,0:46:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.25,0:46:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,爹 你能再教下我\NFather, will you help me with the Greek passage
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.08,0:46:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天那段希腊文吗？\Nfrom yesterday's lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.77,0:46:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特 你不是会背了吗？\NHamnet, I thought you'd already learnt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.28,0:46:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了 因为把课本落学堂了\NI didn't because I left my primer at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.95,0:46:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 哈姆奈特\NWell, Hamnet,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.45,0:46:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你要用心学\Nyou need to take your studies seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.77,0:46:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不努力怎么会进步呢...\NHow do you expect to improve if you're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.15,0:46:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,（希腊语）吾不肯苟且而生 不甘平庸而逝
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.15,0:46:53.57,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在朗读荷马《伊利亚特》第22卷】
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.57,0:46:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,（希腊语）愿成就丰功伟绩 令后世永传吾名
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.57,0:46:58.61,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《伊利亚特》: 荷马(古希腊诗人)史诗 论英雄 战争与命运】
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.38,0:47:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这群小淘气\NYou rascals.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.82,0:47:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们耍到你了吗？ - 当然了\N- Did we trick you? - Of course you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.55,0:47:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们又互换来耍我\NYou swapped places to hoodwink me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.80,0:47:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜 过来\NSusanna, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.14,0:47:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.25,0:47:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还记得要给你娘准备的那件事吗？\NNow, do you remember the thing we were going to do for your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.10,0:47:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯 - 都记得吗？准备好了吗？\N- Yeah. - You remember? You ready to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.61,0:47:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯 - 好 快去 快去准备\N- Yeah. - Okay. Go outside quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.39,0:47:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快去 快去 快去\NGo, go, go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.07,0:47:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 朝那边走一步…… - 等等\N- Just step toward... - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.84,0:47:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一——向右走迈步\NOne st-- Come to your right. Step.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.07,0:47:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,再走一步\NStep. One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.51,0:47:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个\NOne more.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.49,0:47:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们三人何时再见面？\NWhen shall we three meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.59,0:47:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,雷雨交加？\NIn thunder, lightning or in rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.13,0:47:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当喧嚣散去 当战斗的胜负已分！\NWhen hurly-burly's done, when the battle's lost and won!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.57,0:47:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那将是日落之时\NThat will be ere at set of sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.70,0:47:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 地点在哪？ - 在荒原上\N- Where the place? - Upon the heath.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.07,0:48:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,去见安妮丝\NThere to meet with Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.21,0:48:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 格雷马尔金\NI come, Graymalkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.11,0:48:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,牧场呼唤\NPaddock calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.91,0:48:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,匿名！\NAnon!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.45,0:48:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,公平即丑陋 丑陋即公平\NFair is foul and foul is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.38,0:48:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,公平即丑陋 丑陋即公平公平即丑陋 丑陋即公平\NFair is foul and foul is fair. Fair is foul and foul is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.01,0:48:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,公平即丑陋 丑陋即公平\NFair is foul and foul is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.96,0:48:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,悬停在……\NHover through the...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.42,0:48:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好！\NWell done!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.62,0:48:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了！\NThat was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.00,0:48:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,挖深一些 然后把所有东西都移到一边\NDig it deep, and then you move all of it to the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.33,0:48:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把它放在这里\Nand then you put it down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.30,0:48:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧？然后把四周的土也填上\NRight? And then you get the soil around the sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.30,0:48:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你再轻轻拍拍它\Nand then you pat it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.57,0:48:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你就会看到类似这样的片段\NAnd then you get bits like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.48,0:48:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把它揉搓在手上\NAnd you rub it in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.15,0:48:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦然后又回来了！\NWhoa. And then back!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.55,0:48:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做\NDo this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.05,0:48:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,当你这样做的时候 画圈\NAnd when you're doing this, circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.46,0:48:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,对 就是这样\NYeah, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.42,0:48:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好？\NReady?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.92,0:48:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,前进后退\NForward. And back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.82,0:48:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 格挡 格挡 格挡\NNow, parry, parry, parry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.03,0:48:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很好又一次\NGood. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.16,0:49:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 做完这个之后 我要做这个\NNow, after that one, I'm gonna do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.83,0:49:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你赶紧让开\Nand you get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.26,0:49:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗？围成一圈挥舞你的剑\NReady? Circle off. Spin your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.50,0:49:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.84,0:49:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,画圈 旋转你的剑\NCircle, spin your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.31,0:49:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 请上前来\NNow, come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.35,0:49:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,然后回去\NAnd go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.12,0:49:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一二三\NOne, two three.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.32,0:49:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,让开！\NOut of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.52,0:49:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好再次强调\NVery good. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.08,0:49:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思 这个叫什么名字？\NJudith, what's this one called?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.46,0:49:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,百里香百里香——迷迭香\N-Thyme. Thyme. - Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.99,0:49:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,百里香百里香百里香——百里香百里香\N-Thyme. Thyme. Thyme. - Thyme. Thyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.22,0:49:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我搞混了 - 没关系\N- I got it mixed up. - That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.39,0:49:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这个...\NThis one...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.83,0:49:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是迷迭香-是的\N-Now, that's rosemary. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.13,0:49:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,迷迭香有什么用途？\NAnd what is rosemary for?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.87,0:49:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把它放进苹果里——苹果\N- Putting it in apples. -Apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.00,0:49:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不迷迭香是做什么用的？\NNo. Rosemary's for?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.61,0:49:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,回忆\NRemembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.84,0:49:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,回忆\NRemembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.15,0:50:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 你要把这些都揉进手里\NNow, you're to rub all this in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.01,0:50:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你吹了一小口愿望\NYou blow a little wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.36,0:50:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,祝他一路顺风\NTo wish him on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.63,0:50:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？这是你和他之间的秘密\NYeah? And it's your secret with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.24,0:50:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到他了吗？\NDid you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.44,0:50:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你没看到他在天上吗？\NDid you not see him in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.04,0:50:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 再来一次\NAll right, do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.38,0:50:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,再许个愿吧\NMake another wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.94,0:50:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看 就在上面\NLook. Right up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.31,0:50:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 他就在那儿你看到他了吗？\NLook, just there. Did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.82,0:51:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他把你的所有愿望都珍藏在他那颗小小的心里\NAnd he's got all your wishes tucked in his little heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.29,0:51:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 每当你想要缅怀他的时候\NSo any time that you want to remember him,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.76,0:51:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要去……\Nyou just have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.46,0:51:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里？\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.96,0:51:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？我一定要抓住你！\NHuh? I'm gonna catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.21,0:51:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会抓住你的！\NI'm gonna catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.61,0:51:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲？\NFather?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.78,0:51:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都好吗？\NIs all well?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.65,0:51:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.79,0:51:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我希望你远离你爷爷\NListen, I want you to stay away from your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.99,0:51:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会打你的姐妹 但我担心的是你\NHe'll not hit your sisters, but it's you that I worry for,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.79,0:51:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要知道 当我不在你身边的时候 你也能安全无虞\Nand I need to know that you'll be safe when I'm not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.83,0:51:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你要再回伦敦吗？\NYou're going back to London again?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.50,0:51:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 明天\NYes, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.90,0:51:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,明天？\NTomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.60,0:51:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\NIt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.41,0:51:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我们跟你一起去吗？\NWill we go with you this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.34,0:51:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不 还没有\NNo, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.02,0:52:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.52,0:52:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想念你\NI'll miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.05,0:52:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但我必须走了 你明白吗？我……\NBut I have to go, you understand? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.62,0:52:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.92,0:52:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.69,0:52:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那挺好的\NThat's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.46,0:52:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我需要你照顾好你的母亲和姐妹们\N'Cause I need you to look after your mother and your sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.76,0:52:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你会这么做吗？\NWill you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.53,0:52:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.87,0:52:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你会勇敢吗？——是的\N- Will you be brave? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.51,0:52:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是的？\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.20,0:52:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你会勇敢吗？——是的\N- Will you be brave? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.35,0:52:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢吗？！\NWill you be brave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.01,0:52:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？！是的！是的 我会勇敢的！\N- Huh?! - Yes! Yes, I'll be brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.24,0:52:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我会勇敢的我会勇敢的\NI'll be brave. I'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.65,0:52:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我在伦敦看过房子了\NI've looked at houses for us in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.19,0:52:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,秋天来了——嗯\N-Autumn is coming. - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.19,0:52:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们会生病\NAnd the children will fall ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.20,0:52:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思 她还不够坚强\NJudith, she's still not strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.04,0:52:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她经常感到胸闷\NShe often gets congestion in her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.71,0:53:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦的空气……\NAnd the air in London is...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.34,0:53:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能\NWe can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.54,0:53:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但不久的将来 我们会实现这个愿望\NBut one day soon, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.88,0:53:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将和你们一起去伦敦\NWe will come to London with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.58,0:53:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你不会的\NNo, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.36,0:53:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不会来\NYou'll never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.72,0:53:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直盼望着盛夏的酷暑过去……\NYou've waited for the heat of summer to pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.60,0:53:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,秋季的干燥\N...the dryness of autumn,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.93,0:53:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,雪和寒冷\Nthe snow and the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.07,0:53:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你不相信朱迪丝能在伦敦活着离开\NYou do not believe that Judith will ever survive London.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.73,0:53:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你会竭尽全力让那个孩子活下去\NYou'd do anything in your power to keep that child alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.37,0:53:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,难道这不是母亲应该做的吗？\NIsn't that what a mother is supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.41,0:53:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是这样\NOf course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.71,0:53:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.28,0:53:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定在斯特拉特福德以外的地方找块地\N...I've decided to look for land outside Stratford.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.36,0:53:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该带着孩子们住在那里\NThat's where you should live with the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.93,0:53:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 嗯\N- Thank you. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.37,0:54:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哦！\NOoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.23,0:54:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪儿？啊！\NWhere is she? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.51,0:54:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特他就在那里\NHamnet. There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.78,0:54:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.45,0:54:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你我爱你我爱你\NI love you. I love you. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.46,0:54:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好的爱你\NAll right. Love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.63,0:54:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧——我爱你\N- Come on. - Love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.79,0:54:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你\NLove you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.17,0:54:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.97,0:54:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 过来\NAll right. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.21,0:54:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 记住我跟你说过的话 好吗？ - 好的\N- Remember what I told you, okay? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.55,0:54:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子\NGood boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.28,0:54:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,再见再见\N- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.53,0:54:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再见再见\N- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.29,0:55:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再见再见\N- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.81,0:55:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特？\NHamnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.69,0:55:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.52,0:55:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 过来\NCome on. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.83,0:55:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的手牌给我看看\NShow me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.94,0:55:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？你看到了什么？\NWhat? What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.87,0:55:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见你\NI see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.08,0:55:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,长大了\NGrown.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.88,0:55:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,而且非常强壮\NAnd very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.48,0:55:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你在伦敦和你父亲一起工作\NAnd I see you in London working with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.99,0:56:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在剧院吗？ - 是的\N- In the theater? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.66,0:56:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在剧院\NAt the playhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.93,0:56:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我将要做什么？\NWhat will I be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.60,0:56:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特 你想做什么？\NWhat do you wish to do, Hamnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.76,0:56:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该是一名持剑的玩家\NI should be one of the players with a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.80,0:56:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一把剑？\NA sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.54,0:56:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.41,0:56:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我将用它与对方的剑进行碰撞\NAnd I shall clash it against the sword of the other player.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.54,0:56:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看看\NShow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.75,0:56:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,将会有一场恶战\NThere'll be a terrible fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.68,0:56:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所有观看的人都会吓得魂飞魄散\Nand everybody watching will be frightened out of their wits.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.38,0:56:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,谁将获胜？\NAnd who will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.62,0:56:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然会\NI shall, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.25,0:56:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,当然应该\NOf course you shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.64,0:56:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们似乎有什么心事\NSomething has upset them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.30,0:56:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,会是什么呢？\NWhat could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.71,0:56:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,天气？\NThe weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.98,0:56:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是空气中有什么异味？\NSomething in the air, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.94,0:57:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,最好告诉琼今天让孩子们待在家里\NBest tell Joan to keep the children inside today.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.09,0:59:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特·朱迪思？\NHAMNET Judith?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.43,1:00:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思？\NJudith?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.32,1:00:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里？\NWhere are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.06,1:00:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒！\NWake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.44,1:00:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,面包师告诉我 她的猫生了小猫\NThe baker told me her cat had kittens.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.14,1:00:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要亲眼看看\NWe need to see them.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.67,1:00:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有八个 朱迪思八个！\NThere's eight, Judith. Eight!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.65,1:00:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得快点 要下雨了\NWe need to hurry. It's going to rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.69,1:00:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思？\NJudith?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.92,1:00:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,裘德？\NJude?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.46,1:00:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.87,1:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思 你怎么了？\NWhat's wrong, Judith?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.53,1:00:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思 回答我\NJudith, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.81,1:00:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思 醒醒\NJudith, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.47,1:00:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思 拜托了朱迪思\NJudith, please. Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.06,1:01:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是什么人？ - 是朱迪思\N- What is it? - It's Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.20,1:01:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她这样多久了？\NHow long has she been like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.53,1:01:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我放学回来之后\NSince I returned from school.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.54,1:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝：我的天哪\NAGNES Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.70,1:01:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她明白了\NShe's got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.60,1:01:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,难道不是吗？\NHasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.51,1:01:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她得了瘟疫\NShe's got the pestilence.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.01,1:01:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧 妈妈？\NHasn't she, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.92,1:01:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,去找你奶奶\NGo find your grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.25,1:01:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,叫她过来\NBid her to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.75,1:01:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,现在！\NNow!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.23,1:01:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她感觉浑身发热\NShe's burning up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.72,1:01:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要 嗯 更多的水\NWe need, um, more water.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.03,1:01:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,把火烧得更大些 把水烧得更热些\NMake a bigger fire and heat up more water.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.73,1:01:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要热水——伊莱扎 再去打些水来\N- We need warm water. -Eliza, fetch more water
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.90,1:01:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,把贝利斯从厨房端出来\Nand bring the Bellis from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.07,1:01:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一排肉桂\NA row of cinnamon.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.74,1:01:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,肉桂有驱暑的功效\NCinnamon, that's good for drawing out the heat.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.87,1:01:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,松针草或芸香百里香 没错\NPineweed or a rue. Thyme, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.64,1:01:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你会在房间里找到它们\NYou'll find them in the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.30,1:01:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈嗯——另一张桌子另一边\NMama. Yeah. -The other table. The other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.77,1:01:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 妈妈在这里 我的宝贝\NYeah, Mama's here, my love.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.27,1:02:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,来 喝这个这是迷迭香果冻做的\NHere, drink this. It's rosemary and jelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.61,1:02:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的 嗯？\NAll will be well, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.95,1:02:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的\NAll will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.61,1:02:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思 留下来\NJudith, stay with.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.69,1:02:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈在这里没事的妈妈在这里\NMama's here. It's okay. Mama's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.42,1:02:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大黄我们需要大黄来清肠胃\NRhubarb. We need rhubarb to purge the stomach,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.26,1:02:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,驱除瘟疫\Ndrive out the pestilence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.39,1:02:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你能去拿一些吗？\NCan you go and fetch some?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.53,1:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈来了没事的朱迪思 我们都在这里\NMama's here. It's okay. Judith, we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.76,1:02:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜 你也去打些水\NSusanna, draw some water, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.30,1:02:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特和……还有玛丽和苏珊娜\NHamnet and... and Mary and Susanna.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.09,1:02:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,尽快取水\NDraw water as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.90,1:02:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么没来？\NWhy isn't he here?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.94,1:02:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莱扎 去给你哥哥写信 让他过来\NEliza, go write to your brother and tell him to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.74,1:02:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思\NJudith.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.12,1:02:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,张开嘴 朱迪思\NOpen your mouth, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.62,1:02:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,张开嘴妈妈来了就这样\NOpen your mouth. Mama's here. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.82,1:02:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那挺好的\NThat's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.62,1:02:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 你会安全的\NYes, you'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.46,1:02:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你张开嘴 把它喝下去\NYou'll open your mouth. Drink it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.76,1:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,咽下去妈妈在这里没事的 朱迪思\NSwallow it down. Mama's here. It's okay, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.33,1:02:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈来了 没事的\NMama's here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.60,1:02:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.63,1:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.73,1:03:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.20,1:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经尽力了\NYou have done all that you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.57,1:03:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让她越界\NI will not let her cross over.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.89,1:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 您有三个女儿 她们都被夺去了生命\NGrandmama, you had three daughters that were taken.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.23,1:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是……\NWere they...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.40,1:04:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她们像朱迪思吗？\NWere they like Judith?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.66,1:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮七岁\NAnne was seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.70,1:04:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,另外两个还是婴儿\NThe other two were just babies.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.21,1:04:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们身上都有肿胀 而且……\NThey all had swellings and...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.71,1:04:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,像朱迪思一样发烧\N...fever like Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.15,1:04:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈想……\NYour mother's trying to...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.72,1:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看好她的孩子\Nkeep a grip on her child.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.75,1:04:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这行不通\NIt won't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.93,1:04:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,给予的东西随时可能被收回\NWhat is given may be taken away at any time.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.03,1:04:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们绝不能放松警惕\NWe must never let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.04,1:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不要把……视为理所当然\NNever take for granted...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.91,1:04:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,……我们孩子的心脏在跳动\N...that our children's hearts beat,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.51,1:04:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,它们呼吸着\Nthat they draw breath,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.12,1:04:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们行走、说话 而且……\Nthat they walk and speak and...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.35,1:04:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,……微笑、争论、玩耍\N...smile, argue, play.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.45,1:05:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不要忘记 他们可能随时会离开\NNever forget for a moment that they may be gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.44,1:05:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,裘德\NJude.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.85,1:05:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,裘德\NJude.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.69,1:06:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,别难过\NDon't be sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.50,1:06:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你会康复的\NYou shall be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.96,1:06:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会\NI shall not.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.70,1:06:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你 我做不到\NNot without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.52,1:06:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,它在这里\NIt's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.52,1:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,裘德 你看到了吗？\NDo you see it, Jude?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.66,1:06:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它在监视我们\NIt's watching us.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.86,1:06:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉它带我们俩一起去\NI'll tell it to take us both.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.96,1:06:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起去\NWe'll go together.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.84,1:06:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,转身离开\NTurn away.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.87,1:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,转身离开\NTurn away.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.42,1:07:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,它会犯错\NIt'll make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.53,1:07:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它无法区分我们\NIt can't tell us apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.89,1:07:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思 跟我一起呼吸\NBreathe with me, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.43,1:07:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我将我的生命献给你\NI give you my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.40,1:07:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你会康复的\NYou shall be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.77,1:07:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思 我愿将我的生命献给你\NI give you my life, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.81,1:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我会勇敢的\NI'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.48,1:08:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲 我会勇敢的\NI'll be brave, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.08,1:08:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我会勇敢的\NI'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.13,1:08:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我会勇敢的\NI'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.99,1:08:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲 我会勇敢的\NI'll be brave, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.49,1:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我会勇敢的\NI'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.66,1:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我会勇敢的\NI'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.82,1:08:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\NWhoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.63,1:08:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,尽快\NQuick as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.27,1:09:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特\NHamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.88,1:09:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特 你不应该在这里\NHamnet, you're not supposed to be down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.37,1:09:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我得扶你上床睡觉\NI need to take you up to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.36,1:09:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特\NHamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.29,1:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特？\NHamnet?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.08,1:10:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMama.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.88,1:10:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMama.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.72,1:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMama.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.78,1:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特\NHamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.68,1:11:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须张开嘴\NYou must open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.95,1:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的\NAll will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.85,1:11:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他着火了\NHe's burning.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.59,1:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他快要烧起来了\NHe's burning up.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.13,1:11:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,它不会粘住——它不会粘住！\NIt will not sti-- It will not stick!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.96,1:11:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一块石头那里有一块石头\NA stone. There's a stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.73,1:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,楼上有一块石头 中间有个洞\NThere's a stone upstairs with a hole in the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.20,1:11:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,放在他床边拿下来我需要它\NBy his bedside. Bring it down. I need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.46,1:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 嗯 呃 盐去拿盐\NAnd, um, uh, salt. Get salt.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.51,1:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到手了你能送出去吗？\NGet it. Can you give it?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.24,1:11:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮我拿点盐来吗？有多少盐都行\NCan you f-fetch me some salt, as much salt as you have.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.01,1:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,水我们需要水\NWater. We need water.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.37,1:12:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他……他太火辣了\NHe's... he's too hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.31,1:12:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他着火了\NHe's burning.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.84,1:12:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我的爱人妈妈来了\NMy love. Mama's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.02,1:12:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的一切都会好起来的\NAll will be well. All will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.05,1:12:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的\NAll will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.18,1:12:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的\NAll will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.29,1:12:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特 别害怕\NHamnet, don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.57,1:12:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不必害怕\NNo need to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.30,1:12:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的妈妈在这里\NAll will be well. Mommy's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.23,1:12:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈在这里没事的\NMommy's here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.00,1:12:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈来了\NMommy's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.37,1:12:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看我 妈妈在这里\NLook at me. Mommy's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.21,1:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远、永远不会放你走\NI will never, ever let you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.17,1:12:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗？\NYou understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.81,1:12:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远、永远不会放你走\NI will never, ever let you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.48,1:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.75,1:12:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.40,1:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莱扎 把朱迪丝带到厨房去 让她待在那里\NEliza, take Judith to the kitchen and keep her there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.96,1:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,请！\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.20,1:12:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要我！——待在那儿\N- He needs me! -Stay there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.57,1:13:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要我！\NHe needs me!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.04,1:13:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请！\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.58,1:13:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦莱里安……\NValerian...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.78,1:13:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特哈姆内特哈姆内特\NHamnet. Hamnet. Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.45,1:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特 你必须留下哈姆内特 求你了\NHamnet, you have to stay. Hamnet, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.29,1:13:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特 求你了你必须留下来和我们在一起\NHamnet, please. You have to stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.35,1:13:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈需要你我们需要你\NMama needs you. We need you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.06,1:13:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,停！够了！——留下来留下来 留下来\N-Stop! Enough! - Stay with us. Stay, stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.10,1:13:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 哈姆内特哈姆内特 哈姆内特 哈姆内特\NPlease, Hamnet. Hamnet, Hamnet, Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.53,1:13:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,放开他！哈姆内特 求你了！\N-Let him alone! - Hamnet, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.23,1:13:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道看不出来对他来说已经太晚了吗！\NCan't you see that it's too late for him!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.20,1:13:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了\NPlease, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.64,1:13:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特？\NHamnet?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.04,1:13:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特哈姆内特\NHamnet. Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.48,1:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子走了\NMy son is gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.36,1:14:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子\NMy son.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.79,1:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我丢了我的……\NI've lost my...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.86,1:15:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见了光 然后就睡不着了\NI saw the light, and I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.60,1:15:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽在此\NMARY Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.23,1:16:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 孩子 不要\NOh, child, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.93,1:16:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 不 不去睡觉吧- 不 不 让她留下来吧\N- No, no, no. Go to bed. - No, no, let-let her stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.80,1:16:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的错 妈妈\NIt is my fault, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.47,1:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的错——不 不\N- It is my fault. - No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.37,1:16:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思 这不是你的错\NIt is not your fault, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.44,1:16:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但他和我交换了位置\NBut he changed places with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.58,1:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他骗过了它\NHe tricked it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.75,1:16:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他骗了什么？\NHe tricked what?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.38,1:16:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡\NDeath.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.45,1:16:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思\NJudith.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.12,1:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,当他来抓我的时候 他也跟着走了\NIt took him when it came for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.62,1:16:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不要再对任何人说这些话\NNever say those words to anyone ever again.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.96,1:16:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥哥得了高烧 夺去了他的生命\NThe fever came for your brother, and it took him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.10,1:16:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你想见他吗？\NDo you wish to see him?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.67,1:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.51,1:17:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,继续往前走 你可以看到他\NGo on. You can see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.39,1:17:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是他吗？\NIs it really him?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.86,1:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.83,1:17:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它——它看起来不像他\NIt-it doesn't look like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.00,1:17:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.21,1:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不是他\NIt's not him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.48,1:17:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,它不是\NIt's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.15,1:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是他\NIt's not him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.03,1:17:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 现在 还没到早上呢\NIt-It's-it's not morning yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.62,1:17:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有让他做好充分的准备\NWe haven't prepared him properly.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.23,1:17:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我来晚了吗？\NAm I too late?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.67,1:17:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是你——父亲\N- It's you. -Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.73,1:18:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是你\NIt's you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.95,1:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我\NIt's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.26,1:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪儿？\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.77,1:18:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里……\NWhere is...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.84,1:18:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里...\NWhere...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.99,1:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是我儿子\NIt's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.66,1:19:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是我儿子\NIt's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.35,1:19:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看到\NI didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.19,1:20:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该更注意他的\NI should've paid him more attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.63,1:20:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为被带走的是她\NI always thought she was the one to be taken away
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.66,1:20:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,其实一直都是他\Nwhen all the while it was him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.84,1:20:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是个傻瓜\NI'm a fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.71,1:20:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不 任何人都无法救他\NNo, there's nothing anyone could have done to save him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.03,1:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经尽力了\NYou did everything that you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.34,1:20:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我做了\NOf course I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.38,1:20:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你当时不在\NYou weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.08,1:20:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意把我的心挖出来送给他\NI would have cut my heart out and given it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.85,1:20:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意为他献出生命\NI would have laid my life down on the ground for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.42,1:20:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我知道——但没人会接受它\N- I-I know. I know. - And no one would take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.49,1:20:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是你…… - 不 你不知道\N- But you... - No, you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.22,1:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道你当时不在场\NYou don't know. You weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.79,1:20:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他死时极度痛苦\NHe died in agony.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.49,1:20:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.73,1:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他当时非常痛苦——安妮丝\N- He was in agony. - Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.40,1:20:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他哭啊哭\NHe cried and he cried
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.07,1:20:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他哭啊哭啊哭——安妮丝 别哭了 别哭了\N- and he cried and he cried. - Agnes, stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.74,1:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他幼小的身体疼痛难忍\NAnd his little body was wracked in pain. -
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.37,1:20:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不 别让我安静\NNo, don't shush me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.80,1:20:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他吓坏了\NHe was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.25,1:20:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,——你当时不在——我知道\N- And you weren't here. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.24,1:20:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽了一切努力\NI tried everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.88,1:20:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你做到了\NI know you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.55,1:21:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽力了……——你已经竭尽所能了\NI tried... -You did everything that you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.26,1:21:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经尽力了\NYou did everything that you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.26,1:21:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一切\NEverything.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.23,1:21:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一切\NEverything.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.76,1:21:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝安妮丝\NAgnes. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.79,1:21:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我会捎信的 安妮丝\NI will send word, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.72,1:21:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你会传达消息吗？\NYou'll send word?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.10,1:21:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,——给谁？——给你\N- To whom? - To you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.21,1:21:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在这里 - 嗯\N- I'm here. - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.21,1:21:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 我到达伦敦后会通知大家\NWhat I meant was that I shall send word when I reach London.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.78,1:22:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦？\NLondon?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.98,1:22:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须离开了\NI must leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.81,1:22:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,离开？你怎么能离开？\NLeave? How can you leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.45,1:22:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 世界瞬息万变\NThe world does simply not stand still, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.02,1:22:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦有人在等我\NThere are people waiting for me in London.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.02,1:22:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,赛季即将开始\NThe season is about to begin,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.77,1:22:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的公司应该很快就能从肯特郡返回了\Nand my company shall return from Kent any day now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.67,1:22:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在得走了\NI have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.34,1:22:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在？\NNow?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.04,1:22:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有一支旅行团出发\NThere's a traveling party leaving today,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.01,1:22:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还有一匹备用马 所以 是的\Nand they have a spare horse, so yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.51,1:22:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,照顾好孩子们 我一会儿就回来——\NLook after the girls, and I will return to--
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.75,1:22:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,停止\NStop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.96,1:22:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NDon't.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.99,1:23:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,走走\NGo. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.67,1:23:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,当我数着时钟的时候\N"When I do count the clock
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.53,1:23:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“那是用来显示时间的\N"that tells the time,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.50,1:23:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,“看着勇敢的白昼沉入可怕的黑夜；\N"And see the brave day sunk in hideous night;
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.71,1:23:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“当我看到盛开已过的紫罗兰时\N"When I behold the violet past prime,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.87,1:23:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,“还有那银白色的黑色卷发；\N"And sable curls all silver'd o'er with white;
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.01,1:23:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当我看到高大的树木光秃秃的 叶子却不见了\N"When lofty trees I see barren of leaves
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.92,1:23:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,“它曾为牛群遮挡烈日\N"Which erst from the heat did canopy the herd,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.32,1:23:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“夏日的绿色都捆成了捆”\N"And summer's green all girded up in sheaves
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.86,1:23:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“抬着灵柩 长着白色而浓密的胡须；\N"Borne on the bier with white and bristly beard;
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.87,1:24:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我该质疑你的美貌了\N"Then of thy beauty do I question make,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.36,1:24:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,“你必将遁入时间的荒芜之中\N"Thou among the wastes of time must go,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.04,1:24:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,“既然甜美和美丽本身就会消逝\N"Since sweets and beauties do themselves forsake
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.24,1:24:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,“看着别人成长 他们却迅速死去；\N"And die as fast as they see others grow;
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.61,1:24:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,“没有什么能抵挡时间的镰刀”\N"And nothing gainst Time's scythe can make defense
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.75,1:24:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,留着后代 好在他带走你的时候勇敢面对他\NSave breed, to brave him when he takes thee hence."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.11,1:24:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你会再读一遍吗？\NWill you read it again?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.25,1:24:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.95,1:24:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经读过三遍了\NI've read it three times.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.79,1:24:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\NThat's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.23,1:24:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们互赠礼物吧？\NShall we do presents?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.90,1:24:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来自伦敦的礼物\NPresents from London.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.93,1:24:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪 给你一把梳子\NA hair comb for you, Jude.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.97,1:24:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 你得小心点\NMind you, you'll have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.28,1:24:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是给你的 安妮丝\NThis is for you, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.29,1:25:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——是红宝石吗？——嗯\N- A ruby, is it? -Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.56,1:25:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我见过的最好的\NIt's the finest I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.16,1:25:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在谈论那栋新房子\NEveryone's talking about the new house.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.96,1:25:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它是斯特拉特福德最大的\NIt's the biggest in Stratford.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.77,1:25:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,房间太多了 很容易迷路\NThere are so many rooms. One could get lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.64,1:25:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜 钥匙你保管好\NYou shall keep the keys, Susanna.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.14,1:25:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你要好好管理家务\NYou shall manage the house well.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.67,1:25:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 穿上它\NPut it on, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.57,1:25:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,巴塞洛缪带你看过新房子了吗？\NDid Bartholomew show you the new house?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.77,1:25:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.50,1:25:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢它？\NDo you like it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.68,1:25:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不亲自带我去看？\NWhy didn't you show me yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.14,1:25:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是怕我不走？\NWere you afraid I wouldn't leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.85,1:26:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为哈姆内特就死在这所房子里\N'Cause Hamnet died here in this house.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.06,1:26:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我一直在想他在哪里\NYou know, I'm constantly wondering where he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.73,1:26:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,或者他去了哪里\NOr where he has gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.37,1:26:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,无论我在做什么 我都会想：“他在哪里？”\NWhatever I'm doing, I'm wondering, "Where is he?"
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.88,1:26:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 他不可能凭空消失\NI mean, he can't have just vanished.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.58,1:26:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他只需要我找到他\NAll he needs is for me to find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.71,1:26:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定在某个地方\NHe must be somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.42,1:26:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,即使一年过去了 我仍然担心我会因此而发疯\NI fear I may run mad with it, even now, a year on.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.42,1:26:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一年不算什么\NA year is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.40,1:26:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一年不算什么\NA year is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.60,1:26:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,每秒钟都是如此……\NIt's every second...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.57,1:26:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,每时每刻 每一天\Nevery minute, every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.27,1:26:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能永远不会停止寻找他\NWe may never stop looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.04,1:27:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 安妮丝\NI'm sorry, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.68,1:27:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到我说话了吗？我说过对不起 安妮丝\NDid you hear me? I said that I'm sorry, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.21,1:27:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,——为了什么？——为了一切\N- For what? - For everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.75,1:27:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你被那个地方困住了——因为……\N- You're caught by that place. - For...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.12,1:27:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么地方？ - 你脑海里的那个地方\N- What place? - That place in your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.92,1:27:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 它对你来说比在任何其他地方都更加真实\NIt is now more real to you than anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.72,1:27:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,即使我们的孩子去世 也无法阻止你这样做\NNot even the death of our child can keep you from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.30,1:27:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆内特死了\NHamnet died.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.56,1:27:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,死状极其惨烈\NA horrible death.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.63,1:27:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你本应该在那里的\NAnd you should have been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.80,1:27:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你本可以向他道别\NYou could have bid him farewell.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.96,1:27:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了什么？\NWhat do you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.27,1:28:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,唔？\NHmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.28,1:28:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.45,1:28:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么？\NNothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.15,1:28:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也没有\NNothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.15,1:28:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧\NOh, well.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.57,1:28:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该回伦敦\NYou should go back to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.23,1:28:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,您不必为我们操心\NYou need not concern yourself with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.37,1:28:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你 我们也能过得很好\NGet along just fine without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.38,1:28:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这有时是一个悖论\NThis was sometime a paradox,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.38,1:28:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在时间证明了这一点\Nbut now the time gives it proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.18,1:28:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经爱过你\NI did love you once.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.55,1:28:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大人 您确实让我相信了这一点\NIndeed, my lord, you made me believe so.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.49,1:28:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你不该相信我\NYou should not have believed me,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.82,1:28:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因为美德无法使我们的旧血统免受侵害……\Nfor virtue cannot so inoculate our old stock for...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.36,1:29:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你不该相信我\NYou should not have believed me,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.17,1:29:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为美德无法如此彻底地改变我们古老的血统\Nfor virtue cannot so inoculate our old stock
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.00,1:29:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们会好好享受这一切\Nbut we shall relish of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.90,1:29:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不爱你\NI loved you not.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.91,1:29:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是被欺骗的那个人\NI was the more deceived.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.54,1:29:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,去修道院吧\NGet thee to a nunnery.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.05,1:29:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何要成为罪人的养育者？\NWhy wouldst thou be a breeder of sinners?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.38,1:29:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我本人为人冷漠诚实\NI am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.92,1:29:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但我却可以指责我做这样的事\Nbut yet I could accuse me of such things
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.86,1:29:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,或许最好是……\Nthat it were better to...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.86,1:29:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再次\NAgain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.60,1:29:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,去修道院吧\NGet thee to a nunnery.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.56,1:29:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何要成为罪人的养育者？\NWhy wouldst thou be a breeder of sinners?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.40,1:29:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我本人为人坦诚冷漠 但是……\NI am myself indifferent honest, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.73,1:29:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一遍“我本人是冷漠的诚实”再说一遍\NAgain. "I am myself indifferent honest." Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.10,1:29:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我本人为人冷漠诚实\NI am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.04,1:29:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我却可以指责我做这样的事 这样反而更好\Nbut yet I could accuse me of such things that it were better
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.41,1:29:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我的母亲并没有生我——再说一遍\N- my mother had not borne me. - Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.11,1:29:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我本人……\NI, myself...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.72,1:29:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,再次\NAgain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.72,1:29:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我本人则漠不关心……\NI, myself, am indifferent...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.46,1:29:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是我\N"I am myself."
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.09,1:29:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我本人为人冷漠诚实\NI am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.95,1:30:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但我却可以指责我做了那样的事……\Nbut yet I could accuse me of such things that it were...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.36,1:30:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再次\NAgain.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.09,1:30:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但我却可以指责我做了那样的事……\NBut yet I could accuse me of such things that it were...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.40,1:30:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,再次！\NAgain!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.70,1:30:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我本人为人冷漠诚实\NI am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.04,1:30:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但我却可以指责我犯下这样的错误……\Nbut yet I could accuse me of such...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.40,1:30:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是在重复这些词而已！\NYou are simply mouthing the words!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.64,1:30:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我本人为人冷漠诚实\NI am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.88,1:30:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但我却可以指责我做这样的事\Nbut yet I could accuse me of such things
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.12,1:30:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望我母亲当初没生我\Nthat it were better my mother had not borne me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.78,1:30:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常骄傲、充满复仇心、野心勃勃\NI am very proud, revengeful, ambitious,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.82,1:30:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,更多犯罪机会摆在我面前\Nwith more offenses at my beck
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.52,1:30:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我有很多想法想把它们放进去\Nthan I have thoughts to put them in,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.26,1:30:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,发挥想象力赋予它们形状 或者给它们时间去演绎它们\Nimagination to give them shape or time to act them in.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.49,1:30:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 像我这样的人该怎么办呢？\NNow, what should such fellows as I do
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.17,1:30:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在天地之间爬行？\Ncrawling between heaven and earth?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.00,1:30:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是彻头彻尾的恶棍\NWe are arrant knaves all.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.46,1:30:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要相信我们任何人\NBelieve none of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.97,1:30:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,去修道院吧再一次\NGo thy ways to a nunnery. Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.72,1:31:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,成为……\NTo be...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.39,1:31:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,……或者不……\N...or not to be...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.07,1:31:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,……这就是问题所在：\N...that is the question:
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.68,1:32:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,无论从精神层面来说 忍受是否更高尚\NWhether 'tis nobler in the mind to... suffer
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.25,1:32:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,种种攻击和伤害……\NThe slings and arrows of...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.92,1:32:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,……惊人的财富……\N...outrageous fortune...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.40,1:32:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...或者...\N...Or...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.06,1:32:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,……拿起武器反抗……\N...to take arms against a...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.74,1:32:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,……苦难之海\N...sea of troubles,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.07,1:32:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而通过反对……\NAnd by opposing...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.58,1:32:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,……结束他们\N...end them.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.14,1:33:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我祈祷那些树 ♪\N♪ I pray that those trees ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.60,1:33:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我会把我的孩子还给我 ♪\N♪ Will return my boy ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.27,1:33:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 为了 ♪\N♪ For ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.88,1:33:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 可爱的小知更鸟 ♪\N♪ Sweet bonny Robin ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.64,1:33:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 这就是我所有的快乐♪\N♪ Is all my joy. ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.49,1:33:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝？\NAgnes?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.87,1:34:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我……我当时在城里 而且……\NI... I was in town, and I...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.96,1:34:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我想来拜访你\NI thought I would pay you a visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.77,1:34:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,听到约翰去世的消息 我感到非常难过\NI was very sorry to hear about John's passing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.34,1:34:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫怎么样了？\NHow's your husband?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.37,1:34:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,失去父亲是一件……是一件非常可怕的事情\NIt's a... it's a terrible thing to lose one's father.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.51,1:34:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他很好\NHe's well.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.22,1:34:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他很忙 正在筹备一部喜剧\NHe's very busy. He's preparing a comedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.65,1:34:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他的新剧不是喜剧\NHis new play is not a comedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.48,1:34:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一场悲剧\NIt's a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.65,1:34:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道这一点\NBut you knew that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.13,1:34:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,全镇的人都在谈论这件事\NEveryone in town is talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.93,1:34:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就警告过你不要嫁给他\NI did warn you about marrying him.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.24,1:34:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,别假装你关心我\NDon't pretend that you care for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.38,1:34:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是我的母亲 也从来都不是\NYou are not my mother, and you never were.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.96,1:35:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 安妮丝\NGood day, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.09,1:35:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经好几个月没跟我们说话了\NHe's not spoken to us for months.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.67,1:35:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么能……\NHow could he...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.04,1:35:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么可能不告诉我们呢？\NHow could he not tell us?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.70,1:35:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道不好奇里面装的是什么吗？\NDo you not wonder what is in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.87,1:35:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在什么方面？\NIn what?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.70,1:35:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这部剧\NThe play.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.19,1:36:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你在找谁？\NWho are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.35,1:36:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉·莎士比亚\NWilliam Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.02,1:36:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是他来自斯特拉特福德的家人\NWe're his family from Stratford.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.86,1:36:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,上楼去他住在阁楼里\NGo up the stairs. He lives in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.14,1:37:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么斯特拉特福德拥有最大房子的人会这样做呢？\NWhy would the man with the largest house in Stratford
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.67,1:37:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,住在这里吗？\Nbe living here?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.36,1:37:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.46,1:37:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时想……\NI thought...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.50,1:37:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为他……\NI thought he...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.73,1:37:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办？\NWhat shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.98,1:37:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,保持开放的心态\NKeep your heart open.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.10,1:39:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在那儿？——不 回答我：\N-Who's there? -Nay, answer me:
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.63,1:39:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来 展现自我！\Nstand and unfold yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.87,1:39:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,国王万岁！\NLong live the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.54,1:39:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,贝尔纳多？\NBernardo?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.10,1:39:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真的遇到了霍雷肖和马塞勒斯\NIf you do meet Horatio and Marcellus,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.87,1:39:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我的竞争对手们 让他们赶紧行动吧\NThe rivals to my watch, bid them make haste.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.04,1:39:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像听到了他们的声音站起来！\NI think I hear them. Stand, ho!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.64,1:39:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在那儿？\NWho's there?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.85,1:39:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西今晚又出现了吗？\NHas this thing appeared again tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.89,1:39:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么也没看见——霍雷肖说……\N- I have seen nothing. -Horatio says...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.02,1:39:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在谈论什么？\NWhat are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.83,1:40:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切跟我儿子有什么关系？\NWhat has any of this to do with my son? -
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.99,1:40:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人很害怕\NThese men are frightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.72,1:40:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NOf what?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.10,1:40:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们警惕着鬼魂\NThey watch for a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.87,1:40:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼？\NGhost?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.07,1:40:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,……然后铃声响起……\N...The bell then beating one...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.51,1:40:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,和平 断绝关系！\NPeace, break thee off!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.51,1:40:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧它又出现了！\NLook where it comes again!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.24,1:40:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那位已故的国王一样\NIn the same figure, like the king that's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.05,1:40:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看 它悄悄溜走了！\NSee, it stalks away!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.59,1:40:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他\NThat was him.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.69,1:40:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那是威尔\NThat was Will.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.32,1:40:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他没参演——不 不\N- He's not in the play. - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.76,1:40:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那是威尔的鬼魂\NIt was Will as a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.73,1:40:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最后的国王 他的形象此刻才显现在我们面前\NOur last king, Whose image but now appeared to us,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.26,1:40:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,被迫应战；我们英勇的哈姆雷特……\NWas dared to the combat; our valiant Hamlet...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.94,1:40:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,村庄\NHamlet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.64,1:40:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了吗……你听到了吗？\NDid you hear... did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.14,1:40:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.58,1:40:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们喊出了他的名字\NThey said his-- they said his name.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.41,1:40:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\NAgnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.88,1:40:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 等等——让开！\N- Agnes, wait. - Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.25,1:40:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,请安静\NPlease be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.98,1:41:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 他们刚才提到他的名字了吗？嗯？\NWait, did they say his name? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.56,1:41:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让自己难过\NDo not upset yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.62,1:41:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么——他为什么要用自己的名字？\NWhy is-- Why did he use his name?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.45,1:41:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认识他——男：安静\N- I don't know him. - -MAN: Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.39,1:41:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,……并且根据我的建议\N...and by my advice,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.79,1:41:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们把今晚所见所闻分享出来\NLet us impart what we have seen tonight
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.92,1:41:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,致年轻的王子……\NUnto the young prince...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.49,1:41:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢念我儿子的名字试试！\NDon't you dare pronounce my son's name!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.39,1:41:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,安静的！\NQuiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.97,1:41:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,……对我们来说很愚蠢 我会和他谈谈\N...dumb to us, will speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.54,1:41:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我们亲爱的兄弟去世的消息尚未公布\NThough yet of our dear brother's death,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.54,1:41:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,记忆是绿色的\NThe memory be green,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.11,1:41:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 迄今为止 谨慎与自然的斗争仍在继续\NYet so far hath discretion fought with nature
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.79,1:41:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,愿我们以最深切的悲痛缅怀他\NThat we with wisest sorrow think on him,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.12,1:41:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,与我们对自身的记忆一同存在\NTogether with remembrance of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.16,1:41:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我一分钟也不想再待下去参与这场闹剧了\NI will not stay a minute longer to be a part of this jest.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.33,1:41:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下稍等片刻——不\N- Wait. One moment. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.09,1:41:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想回家——我的表兄哈姆雷特\N- I want to go home. -...my cousin Hamlet,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.16,1:41:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我的儿子……\Nand my son...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.97,1:41:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么乌云依然笼罩着你？\NHow is it that the clouds still hang on you?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.63,1:41:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,善良的哈姆雷特 褪去你那阴郁的色彩吧\NGood Hamlet, cast thy nighted color off.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.94,1:41:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要永远用你那蒙着面纱的双眼\NDo not for ever with thy vailed lids
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.98,1:42:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在尘土中寻找你高贵的父亲\NSeek for thy noble father in the dust.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.38,1:42:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,凡有生命的 终将消亡\NAll that lives must die,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.18,1:42:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,穿越自然 通往永恒\NPassing through nature to eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.39,1:42:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 夫人 这很常见\NAy, madam, it is common.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.12,1:42:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但我内心深处有一些东西可以证明这一点\NBut I have that within which passes show.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.96,1:42:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这些不过是苦难的外在表现和伪装\NThese are but the trappings and the suits of woe.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.90,1:42:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持不懈地表达顽固的哀悼\NTo persevere In obstinate condolement
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.13,1:42:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种不敬神的顽固行为\Nis a course of impious stubbornness.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.34,1:42:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不男子汉的悲伤\N'Tis unmanly grief.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.97,1:42:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,它展现了一种通往天堂最错误的意志\NIt shows a will most incorrect to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.02,1:42:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.70,1:42:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太硬了 肉体也会融化\NThis too, too solid flesh would melt,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.94,1:43:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,融化并凝结成露水\NThaw and resolve itself into a dew.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.07,1:43:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说 永恒者并未定下这个结论\NOr that the Everlasting had not fixed
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.91,1:43:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他反对自杀的教条\NHis canon gainst self-slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.05,1:43:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个没有除草的花园 却长出了种子；\N'Tis an unweeded garden That grows to seed;
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.89,1:43:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,事物本性卑劣肮脏 仅仅拥有它\Nthings rank and gross in nature Possess it merely.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.22,1:43:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,事情竟然会发展到这种地步\NThat it should come to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.43,1:43:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但两个月过去了——\NBut two months dead--
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.60,1:43:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没那么多 不到两个——\Nnay, not so much, not two--
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.03,1:43:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如此杰出的国王 真是令人敬佩\NSo excellent a king, that was to this
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.10,1:43:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,许珀里翁变成了……一个萨提尔\NHyperion to a... a satyr.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.04,1:43:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你将引领我到哪里去？\NWhither wilt thou lead me?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.24,1:43:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧我不会再往前走了\NSpeak. I'll go no further.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.25,1:43:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你父亲的灵\NI am thy father's spirit,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.75,1:43:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,注定要在某个期限内行走于黑夜之中\NDoomed for a certain term to walk the night,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.19,1:43:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而这一天 他只能在火中禁食\NAnd for the day confined to fast in fires.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.66,1:43:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我的时间快到了\NMy hour is almost come
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.56,1:44:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,当我坠入硫磺灼热的火焰中\NWhen I to sulfurous and tormenting flames
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.80,1:44:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须亲自上阵\NMust render up myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.26,1:44:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 可怜的鬼魂不 别同情我……\N- Alas, poor ghost. - No, pity me not...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.50,1:44:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但请认真聆听我将要讲述的内容\N...but lend thy serious hearing To what I shall unfold.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.74,1:44:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,列表\NList.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.58,1:44:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,清单 哦 清单\NList, oh, list.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.98,1:44:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你曾经爱你的父亲……\NIf thou didst ever thy father love...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.17,1:44:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天哪\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.68,1:44:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但很柔和 我觉得我闻到了清晨空气的气息\NBut soft, methinks I scent the morning air.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.95,1:44:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,让我独自待一会儿我在果园里安睡\NBrief let me be. Sleeping within my orchard.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.99,1:44:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在我安稳的时刻 你叔叔偷走了\NUpon my secure hour, thy uncle stole
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.45,1:44:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用小瓶盛着被诅咒的赫波娜汁液\NWith juice of cursed hebona in a vile,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.49,1:44:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,倾泻而入我的耳畔\NWithin the porches of my ears did pour
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.26,1:44:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,麻风病蒸馏液……\NThe leprous distillment...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.50,1:44:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,……其影响与人类的鲜血有着如此深重的仇恨\N...whose effect Holds such an enmity with blood of man
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.34,1:44:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,它像水银一样迅速地流淌\NThat swift as quicksilver it courses through
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.17,1:44:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,身体的天然通道和通道\NThe natural gates and alleys of the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.15,1:44:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,它突然变得旺盛起来\NAnd with a sudden vigor it doth posset
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.28,1:44:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还有凝乳 就像……\NAnd curd, like...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.41,1:44:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,…急切地将粪便排入牛奶中\N...eager droppings into milk,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.99,1:44:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,清澈而健康的血液\NThe thin and wholesome blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.29,1:45:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我的也是\NSo did it mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.65,1:45:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一只最快吠叫起来的狗……\NA most instant tetter barked about...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.17,1:45:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,……最像拉扎尔 有令人作呕的硬皮\N...Most lazar-like, with vile and loathsome crust,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.41,1:45:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我全身光滑\NAll my smooth body.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.64,1:45:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 太糟糕了\NOh, horrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.48,1:45:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 太可怕了简直太可怕了\NOh, horrible. Most horrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.81,1:45:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你天性如此 就不要容忍它……\NIf thou hast nature in thee, bear it not...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.55,1:45:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他和我们的儿子互换了位置\NHe has swapped places with our son.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.96,1:45:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.40,1:45:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.28,1:46:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,萤火虫表明晨曦即将到来\NThe... the glowworm shows the matin to be near,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.91,1:46:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,于是 他那无力的火焰开始黯淡下来\NAnd 'gins to pale his uneffectual fires.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.30,1:46:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子\NMy boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.61,1:47:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\NAdieu.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.35,1:47:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\NAdieu.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.59,1:47:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\NAdieu.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.81,1:47:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,记住账号\NRemember me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.70,1:48:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,生存还是毁灭\NTo be, or not to be,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.91,1:48:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个问题\Nthat is the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.32,1:48:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,苦难是否在精神层面上更高尚\NWhether 'tis nobler in the mind to suffer
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.88,1:48:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,命运的无情捉弄\NThe slings and arrows of outrageous fortune,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.68,1:48:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,或者拿起武器对抗重重困难\NOr to take arms against a sea of troubles
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.25,1:48:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,通过反对 终结它们\NAnd, by opposing, end them.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.48,1:48:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡 睡眠\NTo die, to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.25,1:48:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不再\NNo more.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.59,1:49:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,以睡眠来结束\NAnd by a sleep, to say we end
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.83,1:49:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,心痛和千百次自然冲击\NThe heartache and the thousand natural shocks
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.27,1:49:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那肉体是——的继承者 这是圆满的\NThat flesh is heir to-- 'tis a consummation
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.07,1:49:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,虔诚地祈愿\NDevoutly to be wished.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.23,1:49:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡\NTo die,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.74,1:49:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,入睡 或许会做梦\NTo sleep, perchance to dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.57,1:49:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 问题就在这里\NAy, there's the rub.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.78,1:49:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在那死亡的沉睡中 会有哪些梦境降临？\NFor in that sleep of death, what dreams may come
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.28,1:49:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们离开这尘世的轮回之时\NWhen we have shuffled off this mortal coil
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.41,1:49:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这值得我们深思\NMust give us pause.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.12,1:49:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,尊重是存在的\NThere's the respect
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.45,1:49:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,长寿就是一场灾难\NThat makes calamity of so long life.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.59,1:49:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谁愿承受时光的鞭笞和嘲弄？\NWho would bear the whips and scorns of time,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.46,1:49:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,压迫者错了\NThe oppressor's wrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.99,1:49:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,骄傲之人的蔑视\Nthe proud man's contumely,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.30,1:49:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,被鄙视的爱情带来的痛苦 法律的拖延\NThe pangs of despised love, the law's delay,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.70,1:49:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,官职的傲慢和蔑视\NThe insolence of office, and the spurns
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.60,1:49:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那份对不值得接受的人的耐心和价值\NThat patient merit of the unworthy take,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.97,1:49:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,当他自己能够安息的时候\NWhen he himself might his quietus make
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.11,1:49:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,用裸露的锥子？\NWith a bare bodkin?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.27,1:49:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会承担包袱？\NWho would fardels bear,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.94,1:49:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在疲惫的生活下呻吟流汗\NTo grunt and sweat under a weary life,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.42,1:49:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是对死后事物的恐惧\NBut that the dread of something after death,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.38,1:49:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,未被发现的国度 其起源\NThe undiscovered country from whose bourn
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.55,1:49:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没有旅行者返回 这令遗嘱感到困惑\NNo traveler returns, puzzles the will,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.46,1:50:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这使我们宁愿忍受这些苦难……\NAnd makes us rather bear those ills...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.50,1:50:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,警惕！\NEn garde!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.97,1:50:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一！\NOne!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.27,1:50:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不不！\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.11,1:50:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大获成功 实至名归！\NA hit, a palpable hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.11,1:50:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的儿子一定会赢！\NOur son shall win!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.70,1:50:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了！\NWell, again!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.01,1:50:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,格特鲁德 不要喝酒\NGertrude, do not drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.93,1:51:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,又一首热门歌曲！你们觉得呢？\NAnother hit! What say you?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.51,1:51:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就来吧！\NHave at you now!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.60,1:51:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,女王怎么样？\NHow does the queen?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.41,1:51:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她看到他们流血就晕倒了\NShe swoons to see them bleed.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.90,1:52:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 是饮料 是饮料！\NNo, no, the drink, the drink!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.58,1:52:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我亲爱的哈姆雷特\NOh, my dear Hamlet.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.79,1:52:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我中毒了\NI am poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.92,1:52:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 邪恶！\NOh, villainy!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.02,1:52:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嚯 把门锁上！\NHo, let the door be locked!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.75,1:52:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,背叛！去寻找它！\NTreachery! Seek it out!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.79,1:52:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里 哈姆雷特\NIt is here, Hamlet.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.63,1:52:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆雷特 你被杀了\NHamlet, thou art slain.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.67,1:52:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上没有任何药物能治好你\NNo medicine in the world can do thee good.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.10,1:52:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你里面连半小时的生命都没有\NIn thee, there is not half an hour's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.57,1:52:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪国王！\NThe king's to blame!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.28,1:52:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口也中毒了吗？\NThe point envenomed, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.95,1:52:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 毒液 开始你的工作吧！\NThen, venom, to thy work!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.56,1:52:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 你这乱伦、杀人、该死的丹麦人！\NHere, thou incestuous, murderous, damned Dane!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.27,1:52:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喝...\NDrink...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.00,1:52:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把这药水喝下去！\NDrink off this potion!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.43,1:53:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你的联盟在这里吗？\NIs thy union here?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.27,1:53:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着我妈妈\NFollow my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.33,1:53:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我死了\NI am dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.07,1:53:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你活着\NThou livest.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.81,1:53:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,举报我和我的案情\NReport me and my cause aright
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.01,1:53:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,致那些不满现状的人\NTo the unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.01,1:53:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你曾将我放在心上\NIf thou didst ever hold me in thy heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.98,1:53:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时离开幸福\NAbsent thee from felicity awhile,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.36,1:53:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在这残酷的世界里 痛苦地喘息吧\NAnd in this harsh world draw thy breath in pain
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.55,1:53:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,讲述我的故事\NTo tell my story.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.54,1:54:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我死了！\NI die!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.28,1:54:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这剧毒彻底吞噬了我的灵魂\NThe potent poison quite o'ercrows my spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.64,1:55:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,其余时间一片寂静\NThe rest is silence.
